      "description": "Comparison of FEA-predicted construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement against N=11 physical test articles tested at two independent laboratories per ASTM F1717. All QoI differences fall within the pre-specified 10% bound; E/uval < 1.96 for all comparators. The ModelConfiguration used for this validation run is ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which was the release candidate in use at the time of the validation study. The released production build (ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7) was issued as a patch-level update approximately two weeks after the validation runs were completed. Internal solver team documentation confirmed no changes to the structural mechanics solver kernel between rc2 and the final build; accordingly, the validation results are considered directly applicable to the production version without re-execution.",
