      "rationale": "Material properties (E, σ_y, E_t) derived from uniaxial tensile coupon tests on the same Ti-6Al-4V bar stock used to manufacture the test constructs (n=6 coupons, CV<3%). Geometric dimensions verified against coordinate measuring machine (CMM) report CMM-2025-114; nominal CAD dimensions agreed with CMM to within 0.02 mm."
