      "rationale": "One-to-one mapping table prepared (document EIP-2026-002) correlating each simulation input parameter to its experimental counterpart. Measured material properties and as-built dimensions fed directly into the simulation. Fixture compliance measured experimentally and incorporated into boundary condition stiffness. Equivalency confirmed by independent review."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
